1. Project Overview:

1.1 Project Title
EventCase Management Suite
1.2 Project Description
EventCase Management Suite is a comprehensive web-based platform designed to streamline the end-to-end lifecycle of events — from creation and planning to ticketing, attendee management, feedback collection, and post-event analytics. The system targets event organizers, venue administrators, attendees, and system administrators through a role-based, secure, and scalable architecture.
1.3 Project Objectives
•	Provide a centralized platform for creating, managing, and publishing events
•	Enable seamless ticket booking, payment processing, and QR-code-based check-in
•	Facilitate attendee registration with profile and preference management
•	Offer session scheduling and speaker management for multi-track events
•	Collect and analyze post-event feedback to improve future events
•	Generate real-time reports and dashboards for organizers and administrators
•	Send automated notifications (email/SMS) for event updates and reminders
1.4 Technology Stack (Proposed)
Layer	Technology
Frontend	React.js / HTML5 / Tailwind CSS
Backend	Node.js with Express.js / Python Django
Database	MySQL / PostgreSQL
Authentication	JWT (JSON Web Tokens) + bcrypt
Payment Gateway	Razorpay / Stripe
Notifications	Nodemailer (Email) + Twilio (SMS)
Hosting	AWS / Heroku / Vercel
Version Control	Git + GitHub
 
